{"tid":903014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港女煲】150元Ikea易潔鑊與2388元Le Creuset同分","createTime":"2018-11-15T08:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T10:07:32.000Z","uid":150685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1bb9a7a5e289d721b8f2e6250f7c98729e6db66","tid":903014,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:47:50.000Z","msg":"消委會測試市面上25款易潔鑊，發現傳熱速度和熱力均勻度存有很大差別，測試樣本在相同爐具下加熱，傳熱時間相差逾3倍，有樣本在使用電磁爐時，鑊面熱力均勻度的最大溫差高達攝氏139&deg;C，另有九成樣本的的塗層耐刮程度遜色。測試又發現售價150元的宜家家居（Ikea）樣本，與售價2388元的Le Creuset樣本同獲4分整體評分，前者各項目的表現亦較平均，而兩者產地均為中國。<br />\n<br />\n25款被測試的易潔鑊售價介乎70元至2388元，包括12款傳統的淨色PTFE塗層（無石紋/顆粒紋）樣本，9款石紋或顆粒紋塗層樣本等。在熱力均勻度方面，樣本被放在電磁爐上加熱時，韓國EuroCook樣本的最大溫差高達139&deg;C，意大利Berndes樣本則表現較佳，最大溫差為40&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n在傳熱速度上，測試結果發現各樣本的傳熱速度可相差達3倍，在電磁爐及氣體爐上加熱的時間，最快及最慢的樣本均相差逾3倍。報告又指，有動物研究顯示，塗層物料的化學物質或損害肝臟、生殖功能及具致癌性，不少人會擔心塗層剝落會危害健康；但測試結果指出，所有樣本檢出的化學及金屬物質釋出量，均低於德國及歐洲理事會的建議上限，呼籲消費者毋須過慮。<br />\n<br />\n8款熱力較均勻（獲4.5分）：<br />\n淨色PTFE塗層樣本<br />\nVita Craft、Scanpan、美亞Meyer、Lagostina、Le Creuset、Berndes、Risol&igrave;<br />\n<br />\n淨色陶瓷塗層樣本<br />\nGreenPan<br />\n<br />\n8款傳熱較快（獲4.5分）：<br />\n淨色PTFE塗層樣本<br />\nEZ Cook<br />\n<br />\n石紋/顆粒紋塗層樣本<br />\nMagic Living、EuroCook、意美廚Ideale Chef、759阿信屋/Queen Art、尚膳廚Zenez<br />\n<br />\n網紋/蜂巢紋塗層樣本<br />\n雅窗牌e.window、匡橋Concorde<br />\n<br />\n總評（獲4.5分）：<br />\n淨色PTFE塗層樣本<br />\nVita Craft<br />\n<br />\n石紋/顆粒紋塗層樣本<br />\nMagic Living<br />\n<br />\n淨色陶瓷塗層樣本<br />\nGreenPan<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181115/s00001/1542259364654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181115%2Fs00001%2F1542259364654&d=XciyCYDR5ar%2FqBRqMlYw9%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cae5e736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181115%2Fs00001%2F1542259364654&h=b93682cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181115/s00001/1542259364654</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1676758bb745aa4fc57862f7bd93ed404b347872","tid":903014,"uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而兩者產地均為中國</span><br />\n消委會近幾年力推支那<br />\n係咪收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9664765fb7d7c4092efcf65e5758d87b20947f10","tid":903014,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你用撚埋佢"},{"pid":"a8641e9c31782f57e09e8b98ce6fbe9d0df24586","tid":903014,"uid":195169,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1676758bb745aa4fc57862f7bd93ed404b347872","tid":903014,"uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而兩者產地均為中國</span><br />\n消委會近幾年力推支那<br />\n係咪收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"啱先見到有個消委會報告<br />\n話名創優品洗面媲美SKII<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾次啲消委會報告已經係得啖笑, 不看也罷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05427dd3c36f645a26a42a7f9aacea0dadea5ce","tid":903014,"uid":2446,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"其實佢D比較一D都唔似Research<br />\n似中學生做Project<br />\n因為好多因素都冇考慮 同埋冇提出一個標準及合理情況進行所謂測試<br />\n<br />\n例如之前比較廁紙, Tempo係最低分, 話佢唔易水溶 唔吸水<br />\n但冇考慮用家實際使用? 因舒適度同耐用度高先會有以上評價<br />\n<br />\n所以不嬲都得啖笑, 一D都唔全面"},{"pid":"deb7d3ae1e5a9654c75856282222fcbcca9b8c31","tid":903014,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":